.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, cola, almond-milk, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, mirinda
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, italian, american, russian, malaysian, indonesian, pakistani
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, lacrosse, volleyball, rugby, skiing, badminton, water-polo
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, scooter, tram, car, boat, skateboard, bus
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is the russian##1
 3. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the italian is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the colombian is on the right of the pakistani##1
 6. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the right of the malaysian##1
 8. the person driving the car is between the person driving the bus and the indonesian##2
 9. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the roller##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the american##1
14. the indonesian is the person driving the tram##1
15. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the pakistani##1
16. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
17. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the american##1
18. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the malaysian##1
19. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | cola  | milk        | lemonade | almond-milk      | iced-tea     | water      | mirinda     |
| Nationality   | italian | russian         | pakistani   | colombian | indonesian    | malaysian | american |
