10. the fan of dubstep is between the fan of d&b and the person eating grapefruit##2
11. the fan of techno is the person eating apple##1
12. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
13. the fan of jazz is between the person eating grapefruit and the fan of electronic##2
